description:
BIBD Mobile offers you a convenient and safe way to perform your everyday banking needs direct from your IPhone or IPad. With an array of features similar to BIBD Online, BIBD Mobile is the perfect mobile banking Application [App] to have whenever and wherever you are.

This downloadable mobile App comes with an enhanced user interface and is optimised for your IOS device, Features include: 

● Make enquiries on your account balances in your Current, Savings, investment, Financing and Credit Card accounts; 

● View transaction history and get up-to date information; 

● Transfer money between BIBD accounts, locally within other banks in Brunei and also internationally; 

● Pay Bills for all major merchants in Brunei including your BIBD credit cards; 

● Perform Instant Electricity (DES) and Mobile (DST) & (Progresif) Top-ups; 

● Inquire about latest foreign currency exchange rates; and 

● View latest BIBD news and promotions. 

● Mobile Chat. 

Registration to BIBD Mobile is simple and hassle-free, without the need to visit a branch and sign any forms. Simply download the BIBD Mobile Application, provide your ATM/Debit Card number along with PIN and follow the simple steps to register yourself online. 

If you are already a BIBD internet banking user, simply use your existing username and Internet PIN along with the hardware token to start using BIBD Mobile. 

For even more convenience, simply create a mobile password that can be used in place of your hardware token. With BIBD Mobile, you can now manage your finances whenever and wherever you are. 




